{"tid":1533762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「FC，講幾多次要FC」Google doc係人都用得架，仲有9月9就美國國會開香港民主法案啦","createTime":"2019-09-02T21:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T00:58:18.000Z","uid":36984,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b34699a7f4e5b27f2f2e675f81a2fe5cbf60ee82","tid":1533762,"uid":36984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T21:24:51.000Z","msg":"我都係地球毀滅都唔割呀，<br />\n但係可唔可以盡力FC左先呀。<br />\n<br />\n係咪9月9日都等唔到呀，<br />\n仲有承認責任係唔係咁做嘅先？<br />\n<br />\n幫手推"},{"pid":"ba4b19b9e95761101f588e58a0ba51b486e092df","tid":1533762,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T21:27:26.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">堅持下去，團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"57040c414f211eb5972b12eae0564db0369f02eb","tid":1533762,"uid":36984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2